<![CDATA[

  <p>

	  This project contains the jini integration for the bigdata&#174; platform.
	
  </p>
   
  <p>
  
	  A copy of Jini 2.1 is bundled with this project in order to simplify testing
	  and deployment.  In addition there are dependencies on the bigdata project,
	  and on artifacts bundled with the bigdata project.

  </p>

  <p>
  
      See the <code>readme.txt</code> file bundled with the distribution for notes
      on how to deploy a bigdata instance using Jini.
  
  </p>
  
  <h2>License</h2>
  
  <p>
  
  	  bigdata is currently being released under GPL (version 2).  However, it is
  	  our intention to make bigdata usable by non-GPL Free/Libre and Open Source
